OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly dry with variable
OL,6,Famounts of cloud and a few sunny
OL,7,Fspells, best of the sunshine in the
OL,8,Feast. A few light showers across the
OL,9,Fwest. Fresh southwesterly winds in the
OL,10,Fnorth easing down.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be mainly
OL,13,Fdry. Then the rest of the night will
OL,14,Fbe cloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,15,Fspreading northeast, occasionally
OL,16,Fheavy in the southwest.
OL,17,
OL,18,CTuesday:FVariable amounts of cloud and
OL,19,Fsunny spells along with scattered slow
OL,20,Fmoving showers, occasionally heavy in
OL,21,Fthe afternoon. West coast drier later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
