OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry on Wednesday but spreading east
OL,7,Flater. A few early showers on
OL,8,FThursday, otherwise dry, bright and
OL,9,Fbreezy. Rain spreading east on Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
